column5: just a small report from today, went out to credit and finaly third time out with float setup and hooked into nice fish i gotta say its interesting to control the fish on the pin using just 6lb line,  btw thanks to all who helped me in the last couple of days with great info and tips.
Persistance pays off, way to go man.
Way to go, buddy!  Glad to see someone else hook into salmon in the river!
Lookin good man, you put alot of work into that and it paid off.  Next is the steel, if you are out oshawa way at all this weekend let me know Ill be out every day
WTG drwxr Nice looking salmo Thanks for sharing Leechman
